quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,55,"(Woh Allah ki khufiya tadbeer hi thi) jab usne kaha, “ aey Isa! Ab main tujhey wapas le lunga aur tujhko apni taraf utha lunga aur jinhon ne tera inkar kiya unse (yani inki maiyat se aur unke gandey maahol mein unke saath rehne se) tujhey paak kardunga aur teri pairwi karne walon ko qayamat tak un logon par balaadast rakhunga jinhon ne tera inkar kiya hai. Phir tum sabko aakhir mere paas aana hai, us waqt main un baaton ka faisla kardunga jinmein tumhare darmiyan ikhtilaf hua hai"
  3,56,Jin logon ne kufr o inkar ki rawish ikhtiyar ki hai unhein duniya aur aakhirat dono mein sakht saza dunga aur woh koi madadgaar na payenge
  3,57,"Aur jinhon ne iman aur neik amal ka rawayya ikhtiyar kiya hai unhein unke ajar poorey poorey de diye jayenge, aur khoob jaan le ke zalimon se Allah hargiz muhabbat nahin karta”"
  3,58,Yeh ayaat aur hikmat se labrez tazkeere hain jo hum tumhein suna rahey hain
  3,59,Allah ke nazdeek Isa ki misaal Adam ki si hai ke Allah ne usey mitti se paida kiya aur hukum diya ke hoja aur woh hogaya
  3,60,Yeh asal haqeeqat hai jo tumhare Rubb ki tarf se batayi jaa rahi hai aur tum un logon mein shamil na ho jo ismein shakk karte hain
  3,61,"Yeh ilm aa janey ke baad ab koi us maamle mein tumse jhagda karey to (aey Muhammad)! Ussey kaho, “ aao hum aur tum khud bhi aa jayein aur apne apne baal bacchon ko bhi le aayein aur khuda se dua karein ke jo jhuta ho uspar khuda ki laanat ho”"
  3,62,"Yeh bilkul saheeh waqiyaat hain, aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ke siwa koi khuda-wand nahin hai, aur woh Allah hi ki hasti hai jiski taaqat sabse baala aur jiski hikmat nizaam-e-aalam mein kaar farma hai"
  3,63,Pas agar yeh log ( is shart par muqable mein aane se) mooh moadein to (unka mufsid hona saaf khul jayega) aur Allah to mufsidon ke haal se waqif hi hai